NFL team target distributions

fp_team_targets.Rd

NFL team target distributions

fp_team_targets(season, start_week = 1, end_week = 17)

Arguments

season

Numeric. The NFL season. If missing it will return the current year's season. Supported season only go back to 2013
start_week

Numeric. The starting week. Default is 1
end_week

Numeric. The ending week. Default is 17

Value

a tibble

Examples


fp_team_targets(season = 2018)
